name: Gray 1
description:
Christian Dior believed that grey was the most practical and elegant shade. 
The gray color reminds me of the dark cellar in the dacha, where the smell of damp is delicious and there’s a lot of granny’s food. Gray outside the window means bad weather and you can sit at home with a cup of cocoa and a movie. Gray represents calm, neutrality, stability. This color is thought to have a relaxing effect on the psyche, helping to organize thoughts. I like gray in the autumn.
